The Allied Peoples Movement, APM has won the gubernatorial and House of Assembly elections at the polling units where former President, Chief Olusegun Obasanjo and Governor Ibikunle Amosun voted in Ogun State. The APM’s gubernatorial candidate, Adekunle Akinlade equally won his Polling unit where he voted in Agosasa, Ipokia Local Government Area. However, former Ogun Governor, Aremo Olusegun Osoba delivered his Polling units for the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) Obasanjo’s Ward 11, Unit 22, Abeokuta North LG, Ogun State Governorship Results
